{
  "stem": "13457.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, that was the time when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went with my sister to the railroad station to seek trains going back to Rowne to join our parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we got to the railroad station, kid as I was, 11 years old, I decided to have soda.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I left the building where we were waiting for the train and went outside to have my soda.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what happened in the meantime, there, there came literally dozens, if not hundreds in my mind, of German planes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they started bombing the railroad station exactly where I was buying the soda.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was horrendous panic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody started running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I ran back to the place where I left my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember this vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the middle of this huge hall, my sister was standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The hall was totally empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was nobody already there because the bombs started falling, and she was waiting there for me, obviously, putting, [PAUSES FOR 26 SECONDS] putting her own life online.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she was standing there alone and waiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I ran in, and, and at the moment I walked in, we just ran and hid ourselves in a basement of some house near the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the bombs started coming and by the time we walked out from the basement-- the railroad station-- forget about this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It just wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then the question was how to get out from this city and the Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to our aunt and through the employment of my uncle, they got a truck to transport the-- his family out of the city.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
